---
import SectionContainer from '../SectionContainer.astro';
import Eyebrow from '../Eyebrow.astro';
import { ANCHORS } from '../../lib/site';

// §7 About the founders. Single duotone composite (decision G2), responsive <picture> (G1).
---

<SectionContainer id={ANCHORS.about} bg="ivory" class="scroll-mt-20">
  <div class="grid items-center gap-10 lg:grid-cols-5 lg:gap-14">
    <!-- Portrait composite: Anjali (left) + Arvind (right), forest duotone on cream -->
    <figure class="lg:col-span-2">
      <picture>
        <source
          type="image/webp"
          srcset="/founders/founders-cream-800.webp 800w, /founders/founders-cream-1600.webp 1600w"
          sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 40vw, 100vw"
        />
        <img
          src="/founders/founders-cream-800.png"
          srcset="/founders/founders-cream-800.png 800w, /founders/founders-cream-1600.png 1600w"
          sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 40vw, 100vw"
          width="1600"
          height="1056"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          alt="Anjali Suman and Arvind Kumar Suman, founders of ASM Investments"
          class="w-full rounded-lg border border-border shadow-card"
        />
      </picture>
    </figure>

    <!-- Copy -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-3">
      <Eyebrow>THE PEOPLE BEHIND ASM</Eyebrow>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-h2 text-forest dark:text-sage">Two generations. One commitment.</h2>

      <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-body text-ink-soft">
        <p>
          ASM Investments began in <strong class="font-semibold text-ink">2007</strong>, when
          <strong class="font-semibold text-ink">Anjali Suman</strong> earned her NISM Series V-A
          certification — not just to look after her own family's money, but to understand how
          India's wealthiest families build and protect theirs. With <strong
            class="font-semibold text-ink">Arvind</strong>, then serving in the Indian Air Force,
          opening the first doors, she began advising families across the defence community — and,
          by word of mouth, far beyond it.
        </p>
        <p>
          By <strong class="font-semibold text-ink">2017</strong> she was guiding over 500 families
          and individuals, with more than ₹20 crore under advice. That year Arvind retired from the
          Air Force and joined her full-time — a decade of helping after-hours behind him, and a
          fresh AMFI registration in hand. Together they've since grown the practice to
          <strong class="font-semibold text-ink">around ₹50 crore in client assets</strong>, and
          broadened it into multi-asset advice — mutual funds, equity, insurance and goal-based
          planning — for a deliberately mixed book: defence officers, business owners, working
          professionals, and HNI and NRI families.
        </p>
        <p>
          What has never changed is how they work — the partner who opens a relationship stays on
          it, reachable when it matters, never handed off to a call centre. And the practice is
          built to outlast its founders: their <strong class="font-semibold text-ink">two sons are
          now AMFI-certified</strong> and advising alongside them, so the family that started ASM is
          the family that will carry it on.
        </p>
      </div>

      <figure class="mt-8 border-l-2 border-gold pl-5">
        <blockquote class="font-serif text-h3 italic text-gold">
          “We've never measured ourselves by AUM. We've measured ourselves by how many of our first
          clients still call us back.”
        </blockquote>
        <figcaption class="mt-2 text-small text-slate">— Arvind Kumar Suman</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </div>
</SectionContainer>
